\c 9
\s UEzra wenza umkhuleko wokuvuma izono zabantu
\p
\v 1 Kwathi ekupheleni kwalezizinto, iziphathamandla zasondela kimi zisithi: Abantu bakoIsrayeli labapristi lamaLevi kabazehlukanisanga lezizwe zamazwe\x + 6.21.\x* ngokwezinengiso zazo\x + Dute. 12.30,31.\x*, ezamaKhanani, amaHethi, amaPerizi, amaJebusi\x + Eks. 13.5.\x*, amaAmoni, amaMowabi, amaGibhithe, lamaAmori\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba bazithathele emadodakazini azo bona lamadodana abo\x + 10.2. Eks. 34.16. Neh. 10.30.13.23,27. Mal. 2.11.\x*, yaze yaxubana inzalo engcwele\x + Dute. 7.6.\x* lezizwe zamazwe\x + Hlab. 106.35. 2 Kor. 6.14.\x*; yebo, isandla seziphathamandla lababusi sasingesokuqala kulesisiphambeko\x + Neh. 2.16.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Kwathi ngisizwa loludaba ngadabula isembatho sami lebhatshi lami, ngangcothula okwenwele zekhanda lami lendevu zami\x + 9.5. Jobe 1.20. Gen. 44.13.\x*, ngahlala phansi ngathithibala\x + 9.4. Hlab. 143.4. Neh. 1.4.\x*.
\v 4 Kwasekubuthana kimi wonke othuthumela ngamazwi kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ngenxa yesiphambeko sabathunjwa\x + 10.3. Isa. 66.2,5.\x*; ngasengihlala ngithithibele\x + 9.4. Hlab. 143.4. Neh. 1.4.\x* kwaze kwaba ngumnikelo wakusihlwa\x + Eks. 29.41. 1 Kho. 18.29.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kwathi ngomnikelo wakusihlwa ngasukuma ekuthotshisweni kwami, lekudabuleni kwami isembatho sami lebhatshi lami, ngaguqa ngamadolo ami\x + 9.3.\x*, ngelulela izandla zami eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wami\x + 1 Kho. 8.22.\x*,
\v 6 ngathi: Nkulunkulu wami, ngilenhloni, ngiyangekile ukuphakamisela ubuso bami kuwe, Nkulunkulu wami, ngoba ububi bethu bandile ngaphezu kwekhanda\x + Hlab. 38.4.\x*, lecala lethu selikhule kwaze kwaba semazulwini\x + 2 Lan. 28.9.\x*.
\v 7 Kusukela ensukwini zabobaba besiphakathi kwecala elikhulu kuze kube lamuhla\x + Hlab. 106.6. Dan. 9.5,6.\x*, langenxa yobubi bethu thina, amakhosi ethu, abapristi bethu, sinikelwe esandleni samakhosi amazwe, enkembeni, ekuthunjweni\x + Neh. 9.30.\x*, lekuphangweni, lehlazweni lobuso, njengalamuhla\x + Dan. 9.7,8. 2 Lan. 32.21.\x*.
\v 8 Khathesi-ke ngokwesikhatshana umusa wenziwe yiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, ukusitshiyela ukuphepha, lokusinika isikhonkwane endaweni yayo engcwele\x + 9.13-15. 2 Lan. 20.24.\x*, ukuze uNkulunkulu wethu akhanyisele amehlo ethu, njalo asinike imvuselelo encinyane ebugqilini bethu\x + Hlab. 13.3.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba siyizigqili, kanti ebugqilini bethu uNkulunkulu wethu kasitshiyanga\x + Neh. 9.36.\x*, kodwa uselulele umusa phambi kwamakhosi ePerisiya, ukusinika imvuselelo, ukuphakamisa indlu kaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 7.28.\x*, lokumisa amanxiwa ayo, lokusinika umduli koJuda laseJerusalema\x + Isa. 5.5.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke, Nkulunkulu wethu, sizakuthini emva kwalokhu? Ngoba siyitshiyile imilayo yakho,
\v 11 owasilaya yona ngesandla senceku zakho abaprofethi, usithi: Ilizwe elingena kulo ukudla ilifa lalo liyilizwe elingcolileyo ngokungcola kwezizwe zamazwe, ngokunengekayo kwazo eziligcwalise ngakho kusukela ephethelweni kusiya ephethelweni, ngokungcola kwazo\x + 6.21.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho-ke linganiki amadodana azo amadodakazi enu, futhi lingathatheli amadodana enu amadodakazi azo\x + 9.2. Eks. 23.32. Dute. 7.3.\x*, lingadingi ukuthula kwazo lokuhle kwazo kuze kube phakade ukuze liqine lidle okuhle kwelizwe\x + Dute. 23.6.\x*, lilitshiyele abantwana benu libe yilifa kuze kube phakade\x + Zaga 13.22. 20.7.\x*.
\v 13 Lemva kwakho konke okusehleleyo ngenxa yezenzo zethu ezimbi langenxa yecala lethu elikhulu\x + 9.7.\x*, ngoba wena Nkulunkulu wethu uzibambile \add ekusijeziseni\add* kancane kulezono zethu\x + Jobe 11.6. Hlab. 103.10.\x*, wasinika ukuphepha okunje\x + 9.8,14,15.\x*;
\v 14 sizayephula futhi yini imilayo yakho, sithathane lesizwe salezizinengiso\x + 9.2.\x*? Kawuyikusithukuthelela yini uze u\add si\add*qede\x + Dute. 9.8. Joha. 5.14. 2 Pet. 2.20,21.\x*, kuze kungabi lensali kumbe ukuphepha\x + 9.8,14,15.\x*?
\v 15 N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ulungile\x + Neh. 9.33. Jobe 8.3. Hlab. 119.137. Dan. 9.14. Jer. 12.1.\x*; ngoba sitshiyelwe ukuphunyuka njengalamuhla\x + 9.8,14,15.\x*. Khangela, siphambi kwakho ecaleni lethu\x + 1 Kor. 15.17.\x*, ngoba kakho ongema phambi kwakho ngenxa yalokhu\x + Hlab. 130.3.\x*.